    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>《帝国的边界》</i>是<i>冰汽时代</i>的第三份，也是最后一份扩展包。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1147010/extras/266e4790586b8e141f59bc66711af42c.avif?t=1727863340\" width=616 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>“人们认为风雪已过。但真相却是大相径庭。”</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-塞缪尔·罗宾逊，霜冻之地侦察员（1887年，新伦敦）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关于<i>《帝国的边界》</i>扩展包：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为军需仓库附近一处新建哨所的领袖，新伦敦密切关注着你的一举一动，你需要想办法将一切珍贵发现运回总部。寥寥无几的粮食补给以及领导颁布的严苛律法是你们生存的唯一希望。前路坎坷，<strong>每一次的抉择都将带来前所未有的危险与考验</strong>。但是，假如你的侦擦员们能够找到额外的食物来源，自力更生也就不是什么一纸空谈了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1147010/extras/c8303eaaa69fe15bf23946670db8cceb.poster.avif?t=1727863340\" width=620 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1147010/extras/c8303eaaa69fe15bf23946670db8cceb.webm?t=1727863340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1147010/extras/c8303eaaa69fe15bf23946670db8cceb.mp4?t=1727863340\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >霜冻之地的冰封格局正在迅速改变。<strong>你将会遇到其他有着合作意愿的殖民地。</strong>当获得了他们的信赖之后，你就能够与这些新出现的盟友们建立贸易往来，并重新定义属于自己的律法之书，最后组建一个强大独立的联盟，并彻底摆脱新伦敦的桎梏。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1147010/extras/7ac8263904cd06d125219249baa71e3a.poster.avif?t=1727863340\" width=620 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1147010/extras/7ac8263904cd06d125219249baa71e3a.webm?t=1727863340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1147010/extras/7ac8263904cd06d125219249baa71e3a.mp4?t=1727863340\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>《帝国的边界》- 特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >霜冻之地的全新机制：<strong>殖民地与安全路线</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全新外交关系机制：<strong>青睐，改良，贸易，外交</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全新单位：<strong>建筑队</strong>-用于建造贸易站与安全路线</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>霜冻之地上的16处新区域</strong>以及原有地点的全新故事</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>新增3种城市建筑以及7种科技</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无尽模式中的全新设定：殖民地</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由Piotr Musial谱写的总长25分钟的全新配乐（6个音轨）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >众多小规模新功能，改进以及修正</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1147010/extras/f1d77366d9bbcea023e74537cf1d3ba5.poster.avif?t=1727863340\" width=620 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1147010/extras/f1d77366d9bbcea023e74537cf1d3ba5.webm?t=1727863340\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1147010/extras/f1d77366d9bbcea023e74537cf1d3ba5.mp4?t=1727863340\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<i>《帝国的边界》</i>中，你将有机会摆脱新伦敦的枷锁，让往日的那些主子们明白你坚定不移的信念。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Season Pass</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完整版《冰汽时代》<strong>季票</strong>现已推出！拥有季票后，玩家将能够体验自游戏正式推出后的所有额外内容，其中包含三份扩展包<strong>The Last Autumn（《最后的秋天》）</strong>，<strong>On The Edge（《帝国的边界》）</strong>以及<strong>The Rifts（《大地裂缝》）</strong>，三份扩展包中的内容对本体故事进行了大幅度的扩展并且填补了游戏世界观中大量未曾讲述的剧情。当通关游戏之后，你还能够聆听着<strong>Digital Soundtrack（数字音轨）</strong>的精妙编曲放松自己，或者翻阅独家<strong>Digital Artbook（数字绘本）</strong>进一步了解冰汽时代的世界。</p>",
